"""Test modify_initiator remove masking entry."""
initiator = self.provisioning.get_available_initiator()
if not initiator:
    self.skipTest(
        'test_modify_initiator_remove_masking_entry - Unable to get an available initiator.'
        )
self.assertRaises(exception.VolumeBackendAPIException, self.provisioning.
    modify_initiator, initiator, remove_masking_entry=constants.TRUE)
